title: Lydia Can't Breathe - EP (Apple Lossless)
description:
This is a DIRECT CD RIP of the first EP from the metalcore band "Lydia Can't Breathe." This album was ripped and encoded in Apple Lossless (.m4a) format to maintain lossless audio quality and perfection. The format is easily converted to .flac (for people that don't use iTunes).

This EP contains the following tracks:

1. Got Fucked By Johnny Depp On The Coldest Night Of August (0:38)
2. Blue Fights (6:05)
3. It Isn't Pretty Being Ugly (4:14)

Lydia Can't Breathe is a local band in Melbourne, FL. They are cool guys, and put on a great show. This album leaves alot to be desired in the mastering quality, but they are currently working on a new album with all the mastered trimmings. If you like them, add them:
